-- New Zealand Draws With Slovakia 1-1 With Goal in Injury Time at World Cup
-- Bob Bensch
-- 2010-06-15T13:20:26Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-15/new-zealand-draws-with-slovakia-1-1-with-goal-in-injury-time-at-world-cup.html

          
          
             New Zealand and Slovakia are tied 1-
1 in the second half of their soccer World Cup Group F match in
Rustenburg, South Africa.  
 Winston Reid tied the game for New Zealand in the injury
time.  
          
          


  


        